Package at.pm.rs.graphics.dot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DOTDecorator
    The decorator abstract class, used to override the necessary getters and setters with asking for their compositions attributes
    DOTIsAutoIncrement
    This class is used to Decorate a Node with the keyword "is AUTO INCREMENT"
    DOTIsNotNull
    This class is used to Decorate a Node with the keyword "is NOT NULL"
    DOTNode
    The abstract class providing the basic functions of a DOTNode The name to be displayed is saved in the String attribute name.
    DOTPrimaryKey
    The decorator based on a DOTNode, underlining the given name at its getter to decorate it like a primary key should look
    DOTUnique
    This class is used to Decorate a Node with the keyword "is UNIQUE"
    EntityConnection
    The Connection between to Entities (tables).
    Node
    The actual Element, sets up the basic parts of a DOTNode and for getting decorated.
